Sentencas: Nickel-yttria-stabilized zirconia-gadolinia-doped ceria (Ni-YSZGDC) composite anodes were investigated to use butane directly for microtubular solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: It was confirmed that mechanical mixing and sintering at 1400 degrees C for the YSZGDC composites resulted in the formation of a YSZ-GDC solid solution.
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The n-butane conversion for the cells with Ni-YSZGDC composite anodes was higher than that with Ni-YSZ anode.
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, carbon deposition was observed on the Ni-YSZGDC composite anodes after durability test in n-butane.
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: On the other hand, the performance was stable for the cell with the Ni-GDC anode in n-butane due to no carbon deposition.
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The Ni-GDC anode has a high electrochemical activity of carbon oxidation.
Titulo: Direct Butane Utilization on Ni-(Y2O3)0.08(ZrO2)0.92-(Ce0.9Gd0.1)O1.95 Composite Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
